title: Contixo F19 drone
description: Eyes in the sky and experience the fun with the Contixo F19 2022 new released pocket obstacle avoidance drone. The latest engineering in drone technology has built with this drone, with being simple and easy to fly you gain full control with obstacle avoidance and experience all of its features for beginners and experts alike.

title: Holy Stone Drone HS600
description: Holy Stone HS600 drone comes with the 4K Camera, 2-Asix Gimbal, EIS and 3KM FPV. HS600 is the latest and greatest remote control drone from Holy Stone. 4K camera with gimbal and EIS is the latest technology in drone aviation. Equipped with 2 intelligent batteries, each battery provides 28 minutes of flight, 2 batteries support up to a total of 56 minutes of flight, you can charge safer and fly longer. HS600 can be folded and carried with a bag, quite portable for travel. Just press One-key Takeoff to start the drone, and turn on the Altitude Hold function to have a stable hovering, it's quite easy to control all levers. Best choice as a gift for the family

title: Holy Stone HS175D
description: 4K Ultra Clear Camera: 4K camera with 120° wide-angle and 90° adjustable provides a high resolution picture, enable to capture a perfect shot; 5GHz FPV transmission delivery a smooth and stable videos even in high-speed or strong-wind conditions. GPS Auto Return: GPS assisted flight, it can perform automatically return home when the drone lost signal, out of range or low power, never have to worry about flying it away. Better Flight Experience: 2 batteries give you up to 46 minutes flight experience. And functions like Altitude Hold, Optical Flow, Headless Mode, One Key Take Off/Landing and Speed Adjust make it so easy to beginners or newbies.

title: DEERC GPS Drone
description: Upgraded DE22 is a GPS drone with 4K camera 2-axis gimbal EIS, The Gimbal and EIS technology reduces blurring, provides better image stability, you can create 4k/30fps videos with impressive stable and clear footage than any other drones in this sector. And the 4K Ultra HD image (3840×2160p) with stunning clarity and deep contrast, Built in Sony Image Sensor, 100°FOV and 80° adjustable lens capturing a winder and clear view; 5 times zoom gives you a closer look at a distance to get more creative shots. You can just enjoy the flight moment and wonderful images and videos with DE22 Pro.

title: NETNEW S1 GPS Drone
description: NETNEW S1 GPS drone is an advanced drone with two 6K/4K HD cameras and brushless motors. This drone is equipped with two HD cameras. The front-facing camera which is 90° rotatable and 50x zoom offers a 6K HD image with stunning clarity and deep contrast. The bottom camera gives you a 1920P and wider bird's-eye view from multiple angles. In addition, the 5GHz FPV transmission can deliver an ultra-smooth, clear, and reliable image feed for each and every flight. GPS precise positioning keeps you from losing the drone outdoors while optical flow positioning also offers a safe, stable and smooth flight indoors. With 2x included 7.4V 2200mAh lithium batteries, the drone can support up to 50 minutes flight time, which means Less charging but More flying!
